practitioner.about:
Dr. Jacob Cherian K. is an internal medicine specialist with a Bachelors and Masters degree from Bangalore University, India. He has worked as a Specialist Internal Medicine at Mediclinic Al Sufouh in the UAE. Dr. Cherian is a member of the Emirates Medical Association, the Karnataka Medical Association and the Kerala Medical Association.

Dr. Cherian specialises in the diagnosis and management of all acute and chronic general medical conditions. He helps patients with the management of diabetes, hypertension (blood pressure), hyperlipidaemia (high cholesterol), and vitamin D deficiency. He conducts general health check-ups and pre-employment health check-ups.

When Dr. Cherian finds the time, he enjoys watching movies and driving. He speaks English, Hindi, Kannada, Malayalam, and Tamil.
